snippet.title: Suicide Squad: Kill the Justice League | Squad Up, Task Force X ft. Debra Wilson as Amanda Waller
snippet.description:
Squad up! Amanda Waller found four recruits to join Task Force X. Is your squad ready to Kill the Justice League? 

It's up to the Suicide Squad to do what the heroes can’t - save the world. 

Get your copy here: https://go.wbgames.com/AvailableNow
 
Suicide Squad: Kill the Justice League is available now on PS5, Xbox Series X|S, and PC.
 
Learn more: https://www.suicidesquadgame.com/en-us
